---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="The Repeat Offenders | Dining Unhinged">

  <section class="article-hero">

    <p class="article-category">
      DINING UNHINGED
    </p>

    <h1>The Repeat Offenders</h1>

    <p class="article-deck">
      The places we'd happily return to, despite every promise to try somewhere new.
    </p>

  </section>

  <section class="restaurant-grid">

    <article class="review-card">

      <img
        src="/images/og-halifax-donair.jpg"
        alt="Blowers &amp; Grafton"
        class="review-image"
      />

      <div class="review-body">

        <p class="review-category">
          FUTURE CAM'S PROBLEM
        </p>

        <h3>Blowers &amp; Grafton</h3>

        <p class="review-excerpt">
          The kind of place that convinces Present Cam to ignore both his budget and his better judgment, leaving Future Cam to deal with the consequences. A sacrifice he's willing to make.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/restaurants/blowers-and-grafton"
          class="read-story"
        >
          Read the Review →
        </a>

      </div>

    </article>

    <article class="review-card">

      <img
        src="/images/spanish-old-fashioned.jpg"
        alt="Spanish Old Fashioned"
        class="review-image"
      />

      <div class="review-body">

        <p class="review-category">
          LIQUID COURAGE LAUREATE
        </p>

        <h3>Spanish Old Fashioned</h3>

        <p class="review-excerpt">
          Familiar enough to recognize, different enough to remember. A cocktail worthy of another round before good judgment has a chance to object.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/cocktails/spanish-old-fashioned"
          class="read-story"
        >
          Read the Review →
        </a>

      </div>

    </article>

    <article class="review-card">

      <img
        src="/images/pip.jpg"
        alt="Pip"
        class="review-image"
      />

      <div class="review-body">

        <p class="review-category">
          THE EMPTY TANK
        </p>

        <h3>Pip</h3>

        <p class="review-excerpt">
          The kind of place that makes you forget how expensive fuel has become until you're halfway home.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/restaurants/pip"
          class="read-story"
        >
          Read the Review →
        </a>

      </div>

    </article>

    <article class="review-card">

      <img
        src="/images/smoked-duck-mousse.jpg"
        alt="Bodega Ellerslie"
        class="review-image"
      />

      <div class="review-body">

        <p class="review-category">
          UNREASONABLY PLEASANT HUMANS
        </p>

        <h3>Bodega Ellerslie</h3>

        <p class="review-excerpt">
          Ruth somehow knew exactly what we'd enjoy before we did, timed every course perfectly, and made exceptional hospitality look effortless.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/restaurants/bodega-ellerslie"
          class="read-story"
        >
          Read the Review →
        </a>

      </div>

    </article>

    <article class="review-card">

      <img
        src="/images/irish-cheesecake.jpg"
        alt="Made-from-Scratch Irish Cheesecake"
        class="review-image"
      />

      <div class="review-body">

        <p class="review-category">
          IF I DON'T LOG IT, IT DIDN'T HAPPEN
        </p>

        <h3>Made-from-Scratch Irish Cheesecake</h3>

        <p class="review-excerpt">
          Selective lactose intolerance was temporarily suspended while evidence was consumed. Future Cam can deal with the paperwork.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/restaurants/blowers-and-grafton"
          class="read-story"
        >
          Read the Review →
        </a>

      </div>

    </article>

  </section>

</MainLayout>